    <name>VMware Horizon Client</name>
    <summary>VMware Horizon is a modern platform for running and delivering virtual desktops and apps across the hybrid
        cloud.
    </summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            VMware Horizon Client is software that allows you to connect your VMware Horizon virtual desktop to a device
            of choice, giving you on-the-go access from any location.
            Clients are available for Windows, Mac, iOS, Linux, Chrome and Android and may be downloaded from
            my.vmware.com.
        </p>
